Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨下个不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不放晴的话 跟日向的约定就实现不了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才都去哪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个山顶 前峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到满意的照片了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天下雨 周围的景色不好拍…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但拍了花和岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但照相机还有别的妙用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我用下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我们拍一张照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我平时不怎么拍人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉好新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在山里吃到烤鲭鱼 真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了 小葵在富士山上没吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵出了高原反应 富士山爬了一半就倒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在那不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别管我了 大家先往前走…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别提这茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…而且谁说那么害羞的台词了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑通？扑通是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 末明都笑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…太过分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利爬上来 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全因为您送我的登山鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 今天几月几号来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你傻啊 今天不是8月11日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到8月11日？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到8月11日？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今天 我烤了蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向兼职那的铃叔讨来方子做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快吃快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,末明也来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏着皑皑白雪 穿过满天星空的圈谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴里衔着鲜花的他 会不会来寻觅我的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔卑斯的恋曲 让人怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆中的登山家 是温柔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是温柔的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}星が降るあのコル　グリセードで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}あの人は来るかしら　花をくわえて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}アルプスの恋唄　心ときめくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}懐かしの岳人　やさしかの君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32}やさしかの君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱有些困了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要上去睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱 咱们睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵的惊喜庆生会真成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊喜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我心里一直挺没底的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次爬三道岭的时候 小葵是不是真心高兴的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 表面上看着粗线条 但其实很细心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚拉末明拍合照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看着也没怎么为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 一定没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 笑容是能够以心传心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信自己所做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以日向 你也要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我还有个不放心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…承诺兑现了…之后会怎样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了 其实没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦马君和群马酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打架啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今天拍的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴天的时候也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但雨天也别具风情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的视线会原样留在照片上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后回顾照片的时候 就会回忆起当时自己在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿明天晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是跟朋友约好看日出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 跟日向约的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 就是那个最烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 这话说出来我自己也觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承诺兑现之后会怎样 心里很是不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛会发生什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会不会就不是之前的我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片…很久之前就想拍下来的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拍到了心中的景色 那也不是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一定会出现更加向往的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我觉得你们也会永远像现在的你们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远 像现在一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 末明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你方便的话 要不要互换电邮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟你说话 还想看你的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保存完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎下次来饭能玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也要早起 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 晚安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有风声和雨声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天会晴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天会晴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在想同一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 晴天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是雾能散了就更好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来登山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要坚持向上 就总有一天能够知晓答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵你先说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你先说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 怎么办好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 还想去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说这个
